Howdy. I’m a new coder from Team 8006 and am adjusting to both the 2025 code rework and transitioning to YAGSL. I have incorporated the Neo Motor YAGSL-Example code provided by the BroncBotz with minor tweaks such as the IDs for the SparkMaxes and adding the PS4 Controller imports and code to RobotContainer. My code builds, but refuses to deploy into either the robot or the built-in VSCode simulator. Here is the stacktrace. Any help would be appreciated. Thank you.

  • [phoenix] CANbus Failed to Connect: canivore
  • CAN frame not received/too-stale. Check the CAN bus wiring, CAN bus utilization, and power to the device.
  • [CAN SPARK] IDs: 1, Invalid parameter value, parameter id (113) Velocity Conversion Factor, invalid value is nan
  • Unhandled exception: java.lang.IllegalStateException: Invalid parameter value, parameter id
  • Error at com.revrobotics.spark.SparkBase.configure(SparkBase.java:300): Unhandled exception: java.lang.IllegalStateException: Invalid parameter value, parameter id
  • at com.revrobotics.spark.SparkBase.configure(SparkBase.java:300)
